OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777529104
OL,3,CPlayers covering their face during
OL,4,Carguments to be given red cards, FIFA
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FFIFA has updated rules over when a red
OL,8,Fcard can be given in time for the
OL,9,FWorld Cup after two major
OL,10,Fcontroversies in international
OL,11,Ffootball this year.
OL,13,FPlayers can now be penalised with a
OL,14,Fred card if they cover their mouths
OL,15,Fwhen verbally confronting another
OL,16,Fplayer, the International Football
OL,17,FAssociation Board (IFAB) announced on
OL,18,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777529104
OL,3,CPlayers covering their face during
OL,4,Carguments to be given red cards, FIFA
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FFIFA's president Gianni Infantino,
OL,8,Fpushed for changes after Benfica's
OL,9,FGianluca Prestianni tried to hide
OL,10,Fverbal insults toward Vinicius Junior
OL,11,Fin a Champions League game, and
OL,12,FSenegal's team walked off the field to
OL,13,Fprotest a referee's decision in a
OL,14,Fheated and chaotic Africa Cup of
OL,15,FNations final.
OL,17,FThe rule is not mandatory, but gives
OL,18,Fcompetition organisers like FIFA the
OL,19,Foption to use it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
