FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777529104
OL,3,CPlayers covering their face during
OL,4,Carguments to be given red cards, FIFA
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIt was unanimously approved by IFAB
OL,8,Fofficials from FIFA and the four
OL,9,FBritish football federations at a
OL,10,Fspecial meeting on Tuesday in
OL,11,FVancouver, British Columbia, ahead of
OL,12,Fthe FIFA Congress on Thursday.
OL,14,FFIFA's proposal followed Vinicius
OL,15,Faccusing Prestianni of making a
OL,16,Fracially charged insult while raising
OL,17,Fhis jersey to cover his mouth during
OL,18,Fthe game in February.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
