FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777529104
OL,3,CPlayers covering their face during
OL,4,Carguments to be given red cards, FIFA
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FLast week, UEFA handed Prestianni a
OL,8,Fsix-game ban for the verbal abuse,
OL,9,Fwhich it said was homophobic.
OL,11,FUEFA could not prove the racial
OL,12,Finsult, which Prestianni denied,
OL,13,Fthough he admitted using a homophobic
OL,14,Fslur.
OL,16,FIf Prestianni is selected for
OL,17,FArgentina's World Cup squad, he must
OL,18,Fsit out the defending champion's first
OL,19,Ftwo matches in June, although the ban
OL,20,Fcan be appealed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777529104
OL,3,CPlayers covering their face during
OL,4,Carguments to be given red cards, FIFA
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"At the discretion of the competition
OL,8,Forganiser, any player covering their
OL,9,Fmouth in a confrontational situation
OL,10,Fwith an opponent may be sanctioned
OL,11,Fwith a red card," IFAB said.
OL,13,FIFAB also agreed any player who leaves
OL,14,Fthe field in protest of a referee's
OL,15,Fdecision can be sanctioned with a red
OL,16,Fcard.
OL,18,FThe rule also applies to team
OL,19,Fofficials who urge players to leave
OL,20,Fthe field.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
