OL,3,CPlayers covering their face during
OL,4,Carguments to be given red cards, FIFA
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FSenegal players left the field during
OL,13,Fstoppage time of the AFCON final in
OL,14,FJanuary to protest host nation Morocco
OL,15,Fbeing awarded a penalty when the score
OL,16,Fwas 0-0.
OL,18,FPlay was delayed for nearly 15 minutes
OL,19,Fbefore Morocco's spot-kick was saved.
OL,20,FSenegal scored in extra time to win
OL,21,Fthe title.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777529104
OL,3,CPlayers covering their face during
OL,4,Carguments to be given red cards, FIFA
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSenegal was later stripped of the
OL,8,Ftitle by an appeals panel of African
OL,9,Fsoccer's governing body, and the case
OL,10,Fwill now be judged at the Court of
OL,11,FArbitration for Sport in Lausanne,
OL,12,FSwitzerland.
OL,14,FIFAB said the amendments will be
OL,15,Fcommunicated to all 48 teams playing
OL,16,Fin the World Cup starting June 11,
OL,17,Fhosted by the United States, Canada
OL,18,Fand Mexico.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
